The "Course in Applied Artificial Intelligence" offered by 4Geeks Academy is a 6-week program designed for professionals who want to utilize AI technologies in their current roles. Throughout the course, participants will gain a deep understanding of AI and its real-world applications. Topics covered include generative AI, context, prompts, and models. The program consists of 2 live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 12 students. Upon completion, participants will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. No previous experience is required. For more information, visit: [link](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop